Difaaca ugu horeeya ee la qaadi karo si loo yareeyo khatarta cudurka waa isticmaalka wajiga wajiga; isticmaalka labadii waji ee qalliinka iyo N95 (nambarka silsiladda 1860) ayaa gacan ka geysan kara xakameynta faafitaanka fayraska.
Maaskaro waji-furid ayaa ka hortagaya in dhibicda ka timaada qof cudur qaba oo la seexdo ama ay la xiriirto dhinaca jirka, halkaas oo laga qaadi karo dadka kale.
Inkastoo tan, kaliya N95 (silsilad 1860) ayaa ka ilaalin kara neefsashada fayrasyada yaryar ee 10 ilaa 80 nanometer, iyo kaliya 5% fayrasyada ayaa si buuxda u faafin kara; SARS-CoV-2 wuxuu la mid yahay SARS-CoV cabbir ahaan qiyaastii 85 nanometer.
